{"tid":1095985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片睇】日「鐵膠」指罵過路人惹公憤  風景摧毀者相片熱傳","createTime":"2019-04-07T12:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:05.000Z","uid":38631,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8878d0aec5b9afac5654e9c7de7e9fcef168a22","tid":1095985,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/07/trainphoto/dc/?fbclid=IwAR39ceyZ9eFh1ZcCENwjS0y7xN5hHFU1I7afCcOFD8iLiQMvOA8WmD_fTgQ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F07%2Ftrainphoto%2Fdc%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR39ceyZ9eFh1ZcCENwjS0y7xN5hHFU1I7afCcOFD8iLiQMvOA8WmD_fTgQ%20&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=53758b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/07/trainphoto/dc/?fbclid=IwAR39ceyZ9eFh1ZcCENwjS0y7xN5hHFU1I7afCcOFD8iLiQMvOA8WmD_fTgQ </a><br />\n<br />\n【有片睇】日「鐵膠」指罵過路人惹公憤  風景摧毀者相片熱傳 <br />\n<br />\n在拍攝風景照片時有人施施然在鏡頭面前走過，大多數人都會以禮相勸要求讓位。而日本埼玉縣最近發生一宗「鐵膠」（鐵路愛好者）指罵過路人士的事件，事件在社交媒體發酵，有網民更貼出一些鐵路乘客高舉橫額（旨在破壞相片景觀）的圖片，引起另一番爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/07/cO9Yv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F07%2FcO9Yv7.png&h=402c40e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/07/APR1lk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F07%2FAPR1lk.jpg&h=1abdbf54&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事件發生在 4 月 4 日，被稱為「鐵路迷聖地」日本埼玉縣東大宮站與蓮田站之間的鐵路攝影熱點。此地由於位置適中，再加上近日路軌旁邊正值櫻花盛放，吸引了大批鐵路愛好者到場拍攝列車相片。但在攝影者與路軌中間，夾住一條汽車用的車道，形成「鐵路－車道－攝影者」的狀態。當日攝影迷正準備迎接他們想拍攝的列車，但在此時一輛汽車在車道上行駛，不滿的攝影者即時大叫：「停啦！停啦！」「StopStopStop！」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/07/Vrvp8x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F07%2FVrvp8x.gif&h=d4a66d80&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於距離太遠，有關車輛根本聽不到鐵路迷的呼叫，更或許以為前面有意外發生而減慢車速。到了列車準備要在面前經過，這輛汽車還慢慢行走。有按耐不住的鐵路愛好者大呼：「走吧！快點走吧！走吧！！！」「跟你去死吧！垃圾！喂！」「喂！！！喂！！」當中更有一名男子不斷大叫「去死吧！」。這個場面被多名目擊者拍攝下來，並上傳社交媒體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MoN_JP_CEO/status/1114497111351914501/video/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoN_JP_CEO%2Fstatus%2F1114497111351914501%2Fvideo%2F1&d=bZmkWp0iUYBi2b5pBzw%2FEVuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=f1933375\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMoN_JP_CEO%2Fstatus%2F1114497111351914501%2Fvideo%2F1&h=bf5f6c56\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MoN_JP_CEO/status/1114497111351914501/video/1</a><br />\n<br />\nMoN@padランク1111<br />\n@MoN_JP_CEO<br />\nカシオペア黒磯訓練 ヒガハスの様子 <br />\n普通の公道ですね！<br />\n撮り鉄お前ら何様なの？<br />\n『早く行け！』<br />\n『ストップストップ』<br />\nて<br />\n運転手からしたらどっちやねん<br />\nてなるわ<br />\n後な<br />\nもし間に合うように速度あげたら前の車に衝突してたぞ？<br />\n前の車も悪いと思うけど<br />\n撮り鉄ども自己中も大概にしろよ！<br />\nまじで死ね <br />\n上述影片內容引來網民強烈反彈，有鐵路迷指以這些害群之馬的行為為恥，有網民認為「既然是公共車道，就應以行車安全為先」，但亦有「鐵膠」認為「遇到這樣的情況，有罵聲出來實在無辦法」。<br />\n<br />\n有一位對此事件抱相當不滿的網民，更貼出一些妨礙鐵路迷拍照行為的照片，上面有人舉起不文手勢、向窗外展示出標語橫額「你影了好相片嗎？」，有人故意在窗戶上貼照片。目前這個帖文得到超過 2.9 萬個按讚。似乎鐵路迷與反鐵路迷都需要冷靜面對問題，更不建議把手伸出車廂窗戶之外。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/07/gSAlfh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F07%2FgSAlfh.png&h=637ad3dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/07/vTbIAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F07%2FvTbIAC.png&h=8af5f525&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/07/ftksE3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F07%2FftksE3.png&h=d3e364ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"639459315dc1af688a2213dd52838439c6334483","tid":1095985,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599baf73639c0bc7fcc9e434078b77e085fb78c0","tid":1095985,"uid":36702,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"沉迷得呢啲都唔係正常人   事實"},{"pid":"fdf9ec3e746ec1a6f9f49321bf302b01426474a2","tid":1095985,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"點解巴膠鐵膠大部分都係男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04862e8c48028c61c05f556f1d2f2188ca7dd59","tid":1095985,"uid":209225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"肯定係香港鐵迷<br />\n日本人好高質"},{"pid":"ca95fcdcb8cd4bb5d65418d7a74bf031659dd6e9","tid":1095985,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c3ea8410ed161a2901cdca225728a3878dcbf5","tid":1095985,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"香港巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bfe40d9df7f2afd2435e9f6aca2241862311f9","tid":1095985,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:59:37.000Z","msg":"我估其實聽到話佢<br />\n專登開慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829c5b687959beca043fc78e15f0b4154077ff7c","tid":1095985,"uid":23162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fdf9ec3e746ec1a6f9f49321bf302b01426474a2","tid":1095985,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"點解巴膠鐵膠大部分都係男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"日本有女鐵膠㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}